name: Extracted
description: Extracted is a movie starring Sasha Roiz, Jenny Mollen, and Dominic Bogart. A scientist who has invented a technology to construct virtual realities from people's memories finds himself in a perilous situation, after he reluctantly...

review.name: Much, much, better than it's rating.
review.reviewBody:
I'm taking the time to review this, which I often do not, considering I watch every movie that is released, because the rating on this movie is far to low. It's definitely not a 9 ( my rating standard is tough, ) which I have given it, but it's definitely far from a 5; I gave it a 9 in the hopes it's overall rating would be raised.

Anyways, how people are giving this such a bad rating are beyond me. Everything that you expect in a movie was there, great character portrayals, great writing, and obviously good direction. This director/writer I'll definitely be keeping an eye to see what he can do wit a bigger budget. Great work.

trailer.name: Theatrical Trailer
trailer.description: A scientist invents a technique to enter people's memories deep within their subconscious when their mind is at its most vulnerable state. When he is tasked with entering a convicted criminal's mind to see whether he committed murder, he is faced with his most dangerous and risky memory extraction ever.
